CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1778842974
OL,3,CIndecent exposure on the rise as
OL,4,Cvictims claim it's too often dismissed
OL,6,FKeeping what had happened to himself
OL,7,Fweighed heavily on his shoulders. He
OL,8,Ftold me that, initially, he had
OL,9,Fremained silent out of fear. However,
OL,10,Fwith time, the burden of the secret
OL,11,Fgrew heavier.
OL,13,F"It was more embarrassment than
OL,14,Fanything, especially being a male,
OL,15,Fwhich is absolutely wrong.
OL,17,F"My mother used to say; 'When you were
OL,18,Faround seven or eight years old, you
OL,19,Fchanged, you were a different boy'.
OL,20,FIt's dictated my behaviour throughout
OL,21,Flife. I don't trust people."
OL,26,@uD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1778842974
OL,3,CIndecent exposure on the rise as
OL,4,Cvictims claim it's too often dismissed
OL,6,FUnable to process the incident, he
OL,7,Fturned to drugs and alcohol.
OL,9,F"I couldn't deal with the inner demons
OL,10,Fat the time. The build up of the
OL,11,Fincident is a scar that never heals
OL,12,Fand because of that, the scar was
OL,13,Fgetting bigger and deeper.
OL,15,F"I wanted to leave the world because I
OL,16,Fcouldn't cope with it anymore."
OL,26,@qD@AOUwD@AOUxD@_O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/12
