CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1778842974
OL,3,CIndecent exposure on the rise as
OL,4,Cvictims claim it's too often dismissed
OL,6,FAt breaking point, David finally
OL,7,Fdecided to confide in the charity New
OL,8,FPathways, who provide specialist
OL,9,Fsupport for adults, children and young
OL,10,Fpeople who have been affected by rape,
OL,11,Fsexual assault or abuse.
OL,13,FA decision he told me saved his life.
OL,15,FSpeaking to professionals about what
OL,16,Fhad happened to him gave him the
OL,17,Fconfidence to finally open up to
OL,18,Fcertain members of his family,
OL,19,Falleviating the burden after half a
OL,20,Fcentury of silence.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
