PN,46210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1778842974
OL,3,CIndecent exposure on the rise as
OL,4,Cvictims claim it's too often dismissed
OL,6,FAnna explained how she often feels
OL,7,Ffrustrated when she sees comments on
OL,8,Fsocial media 'making light' of
OL,9,Fexposure.
OL,11,FFor her, the consequences of this
OL,12,Fcrime have given her "no choice" but
OL,13,Fto change her behaviour in order to
OL,14,Ffeel safe.
OL,16,F"Even now, I find myself being very
OL,17,Faware if someone is walking a few feet
OL,18,Fbehind me. Even in broad daylight, if
OL,19,FI'm just walking to the shop, I check
OL,20,Fover my shoulder."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
