PN,46211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1778842974
OL,3,CIndecent exposure on the rise as
OL,4,Cvictims claim it's too often dismissed
OL,6,FA spokesperson from the Home Office
OL,7,Fsaid: "This Government has pledged to
OL,8,Fhalve all forms of violence against
OL,9,Fwomen and girls within a decade. This
OL,10,Fincludes exposure and voyeurism which
OL,11,Fare often incorrectly dismissed as
OL,12,Fless serious.
OL,14,F"We are reviewing how the police
OL,15,Frespond to non-contact sexual offences
OL,16,Fand have supported the development of
OL,17,Fnew training for police on these
OL,18,Fcrimes, but we know there is further
OL,19,Fto go to ensure survivors report these
OL,20,Foffences and are taken seriously when
OL,21,Fthey do."
OL,26,@oD@GOUvD@AOU}D@IO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/12
