OL,3,CIndecent exposure on the rise as
OL,4,Cvictims claim it's too often dismissed
OL,6,FAnna and David are just two voices out
OL,7,Fof hundreds across the country who
OL,8,Fhave been impacted by exposure and for
OL,9,Fthose living with the aftermath, even
OL,10,Fa brief moment, can shape a lifetime.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/12
